==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: xīn fú kŏu fú
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: sim-ho̍k-kháu-ho̍k
===Idiom===
'''[[心]][[服]][[口]][[服]]'''
# to sincerely yield to another's superiority; cry uncle; to be won over completely
#: ''[[科比]][[不负众望]]“[[镇压]]”[[嘘声]][[让]][[丹佛]][[球迷]]'''心服口服''''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''[[科比]][[不負眾望]]“[[鎮壓]]”[[噓聲]][[讓]][[丹佛]][[球迷]]'''心服口服''''' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''[[wikipedia:Kobe Bryant|Kobe Bryant]] does not disappoint, "silences" the booing and '''wins over''' the Denver fans''

